Buddycloud-build
================

buddycloud-build is a set of scripts for managing the build, packaging, and archiving of buddycloud-related projects.

Basic config is set in the file 'system.d/conf.d/config.sh' . There are other config files in the dirs under conf.d.

For usage see the file 'doc/usage.txt'

The main program file is 'system.d/bc-build.sh' . You should create a symlink to this in your $PATH.
